4
00:00:21,275 --> 00:00:23,567
[gasps] Nothing, never mind!

5
00:00:25,817 --> 00:00:28,525
[SATSUMA] Here! I apologize
for my friend's rudeness.

6
00:00:28,608 --> 00:00:30,483
Uh, it's cool, bye!

7
00:00:30,567 --> 00:00:32,608
[SATSUMA] He looked like
he was afraid for his life.

8
00:00:32,692 --> 00:00:34,233
What do you have to
say for yourself?

9
00:00:34,317 --> 00:00:36,733
Oh, lay off!
Who the hell cares anyway?

10
00:00:36,817 --> 00:00:38,650
It wouldn't kill you
to be a little more polite

11
00:00:38,733 --> 00:00:39,983
to the people
around you, you know.

12
00:00:40,067 --> 00:00:42,400
Otherwise, you're going
to keep making enemies.

13
00:00:42,483 --> 00:00:44,608
Please. If they're gonna
hate somebody based on

14
00:00:44,692 --> 00:00:46,733
a one word interaction,
then who needs 'em?

15
00:00:46,817 --> 00:00:50,358
[SATUSMA sighs] Must you be so
quick to push others away?

16
00:00:50,442 --> 00:00:51,983
Don't you want to
have more friends?

17
00:00:52,067 --> 00:00:55,525
Listen! If I've got
free time to waste,

18
00:00:55,608 --> 00:00:58,483
I'm gonna spend it with
some kitties, not people!

19
00:00:58,567 --> 00:01:01,108
My loves! Come to me!

20
00:01:01,192 --> 00:01:04,817
[CATS meowing]

21
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:05,983
See? Look, I've
got enough friends

22
00:01:06,067 --> 00:01:07,608
to form a club of my own!

23
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:09,233
We'll call ourselves
"Ryo and the Pussycats"!

24
00:01:09,317 --> 00:01:10,067
How 'bout that?

25
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:12,150
Do whatever you want.

26
00:01:12,233 --> 00:01:14,275
Heh. Well, someone's jealous.

27
00:01:14,358 --> 00:01:16,483
[BLACK CAT meows]

28
00:01:16,567 --> 00:01:19,317
Careful with the claws there,
black kitty, I've got ya!

29
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,733
Who's my baby kit
cat snick snack?

30
00:02:55,775 --> 00:02:59,192
[CATS meowing]

31
00:02:59,275 --> 00:03:01,150
Apparently, poor Mike
is still having

32
00:03:01,233 --> 00:03:03,067
