a rare prize!

33
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:05,858
Kai is so adorably
straightforward!

34
00:03:05,942 --> 00:03:07,358
[MALE PLAYER 9A]
What was up with the honey toast

35
00:03:07,442 --> 00:03:10,108
at that karaoke place?
It was sliced so thin!

36
00:03:10,192 --> 00:03:12,733
[FEMALE PLAYER 9C sighs]
I wanna hear Saku sing.

37
00:03:12,817 --> 00:03:16,608
[EILMUND] No fair! I wanna
go play with Sosuke, too!

38
00:03:16,692 --> 00:03:18,692
I know Ryo seems a little
rough around the edges

39
00:03:18,775 --> 00:03:20,858
at first, but he's
actually really nice!

40
00:03:20,942 --> 00:03:22,567
He even wakes up in
the middle of the night

41
00:03:22,650 --> 00:03:25,108
to change my water bowl,
it's so sweet!

42
00:03:25,192 --> 00:03:27,358
